description: This file contains implementations for ASN.1 objects related to X.509 extensions, such as Extensions, Extension, AuthorityKeyIdentifier, KeyIdentifier, GeneralNames, GeneralName, ORAddress, EDIPartyName, KeyUsage, ExtKeyUsageSyntax, BasicConstraints, PrivateKeyUsagePeriod, CertificatePolicies, PolicyInformation, etc. It includes creation, validation, and helper functions for ASN.1 structures used in certificate extensions.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_EXTENSIONS
classes.description: Represents a sequence of Extension objects, corresponding to the Extensions ASN.1 type.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_EXTENSION
classes.description: Represents a single Extension ASN.1 object containing extnID, critical flag, and extnValue.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_AUTHORITYKEYIDENTIFIER
classes.description: Represents the AuthorityKeyIdentifier ASN.1 structure with optional keyIdentifier, authorityCertIssuer, and serialNumber.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_KEYIDENTIFIER
classes.description: OctetString-based identifier for public key.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_GENERALNAMES
classes.description: Sequence of GeneralName objects, representing various identities or addresses.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_GENERALNAME
classes.description: Choice type representing various forms of general names such as rfc822Name, dNSName, URI, IPAddress, etc.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_ORADDRESS
classes.description: OctetString-based representation of an address.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_EDIPARTYNAME
classes.description: Sequence with optional nameAssigner and partyName fields.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_KEYUSAGE
classes.description: BitString indicating key usages such as digitalSignature, keyEncipherment, etc.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_EXTKEYUSAGESYNTAX
classes.description: Sequence of OID representing extended key usages.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_BASICCONSTRAINTS
classes.description: Sequence containing cA boolean and optional pathLenConstraint.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_PRIVATEKEYUSAGEPERIOD
classes.description: Sequence with optional notBefore and notAfter GeneralizedTime fields.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_CERTIFICATEPOLICIES
classes.description: Sequence of PolicyInformation objects.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_POLICYINFORMATION
classes.description: Sequence containing policyIdentifier and policyQualifiers.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_POLICYINFORMATION
classes.description: Represents the ASN.1 structure for PolicyInformation containing policyIdentifier and policyQualifiers.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_POLICYQUALIFIERS
classes.description: Represents a sequence of PolicyQualifierInfo objects.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_POLICYQUALIFIERINFO
classes.description: Represents each PolicyQualifierInfo, containing policyQualifierID and qualifier.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_POLICYQUALIFIER
classes.description: Choice type for policy qualifiers, either userNotice or cpsuri.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_USERNOTICE
classes.description: Sequence with noticeRef and explicitText.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_NOTICEREFERENCE
classes.description: Sequence with organization and noticeNumbers.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_DISPLAYTEXT
classes.description: Choice of visibleString, bmpString, utf8String, or ia5String.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_POLICYMAPPINGS
classes.description: Sequence of PolicyMapping objects.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_NAMECONSTRAINTS
classes.description: Sequence with permittedSubtrees and excludedSubtrees.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_GENERALSUBTREES
classes.description: Sequence of GeneralSubTree objects.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_GENERALSUBTREE
classes.description: Sequence with base, minimum, maximum.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_POLICYCONSTRAINTS
classes.description: Sequence of requireExplicitPolicy and inhibitPolicyMapping.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_SUBJECTDIRECTORYATTRIBUTES
classes.description: Sequence of Attribute objects.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_CRLNUMBER
classes.description: Integer representing CRLNumber.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_CRLDISTPOINTSSYNTAX
classes.description: Sequence of DistributionPoint objects.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_DISTRIBUTIONPOINT
classes.description: Sequence with distributionPoint, reasons, cRLIssuer.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_DISTRIBUTIONPOINTNAME
classes.description: Choice of fullName or nameRelativeToCRLIssuer.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_REASONFLAGS
classes.description: BitString for ReasonFlags.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_ISSUINGDISTRIBUTIONPOINT
classes.description: Sequence with distributionPoint, onlyConstrainsUserCerts, onlyConstrainsCACerts, onlySomeReasons, indirectCRL.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_EXTENSIONVALUE
classes.description: Choice type wrapping various ASN.1 extension structures such as AuthorityKeyIdentifier, KeyUsage, etc., with functions for selection, validation, and OID/Mask mapping.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE AnscAsn1CreateExtensions(ANSC_HANDLE hReserved)
methods.description: Creates an Extensions ASN.1 object, which is a sequence of Extension objects.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE AnscAsn1CreateExtension(ANSC_HANDLE hReserved)
methods.description: Creates a single Extension ASN.1 object with fields for extnID, critical, and extnValue.

methods.name: AnscAsn1CreateOctetString
methods.description: Creates an octet string ASN.1 object.

methods.name: AnscAsn1CreateSequenceOf
methods.description: Creates a sequence of ASN.1 objects.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE AnscAsn1CreatePolicyInformation(ANSC_HANDLE hReserved)
methods.description: Creates an ASN.1 PolicyInformation object with initialize functions and child creation.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE AnscAsn1CreateUserNotice(ANSC_HANDLE hReserved)
methods.description: Creates UserNotice ASN.1 sequence with noticeRef and explicitText.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE AnscAsn1CreateDisplayText(ANSC_HANDLE hReserved)
methods.description: Creates DisplayText ASN.1 choice holding different string types.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE AnscAsn1CreateExtensionValue(ANSC_HANDLE hReserved)
methods.description: Creates base ASN.1 choice object that can represent various X.509 extension values like key identifiers, policies, constraints, etc., with selection and mapping functions.

methods.name: AnscAsn1ExtensionValueCreateSelection
methods.description: Selects specific ASN.1 structures based on index or OID for ExtensionValue.

methods.name: AnscAsn1ExtensionValueGetSelectionName
methods.description: Returns the name of the selection type for ExtensionValue based on index.

methods.name: AnscAsn1ExtensionValueGetOIDValueByMask
methods.description: Maps selection mask to corresponding OID string.

methods.name: AnscAsn1ExtensionValueGetChoiceByOID
methods.description: Returns the selection mask corresponding to a given OID string.

methods.name: AnscAsn1ExtensionValueGetOIDValueByMask
methods.description: Returns the string representation of the OID corresponding to the provided extension value mask type.
